,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"回想起来，\n以前的Roselia，大家的关系很生硬","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev97-me4-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"相处起来顾虑很多，太过客气……\n就算想和其他成员拉近关系，还是会在心里留出距离","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev97-me4-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"当然，那种生硬的阶段，\n对我们来说也是必不可少的！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev97-me4-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"但是啊，之前去主题公园的时候，\n那种生硬和客气的气氛\n好像没有多少了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev97-me4-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"亚子和燐子拜托我们帮忙。\n我们也是一边嘴上说着『拿你们没办法』，\n一边觉得帮她们是理所当然的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev97-me4-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"每个人都竭尽全力去做自己力所能及的事情，\n朝着同一个目标前面，到达终点时发自内心地感到高兴……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev97-me4-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"我们渐渐习惯这种状态，\n让我觉得非常高兴","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev97-me4-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"我不禁觉得，\n这或许就是成长","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev97-me4-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId